metadata.name: Optimus Force - ETH #1
metadata.description: In the future Robots will be more intelligent with artificial intelligence, deep programming and a wide range of sensors will be added to AI-powered robots, including vision devices like vibration sensors, proximity sensors, accelerometers, and other environmental sensors, to provide them with sensing information they can process and act upon in real-time. And even some robots will think that humans create technological problems, in turn they will try to destroy humankind. But some robots will come from the future to save the humans. These Robots will Be called Optimus Force!
